trans-unit.source: Clear-Item
trans-unit.target: Clear-Item

trans-unit.source: Clear-Item
trans-unit.target: Clear-Item

trans-unit.source: SYNOPSIS
trans-unit.target: 概要

trans-unit.source: Clears the contents of an item, but does not delete the item.
trans-unit.target: 清除某個項目的內容，但不會刪除項目。

trans-unit.source: SYNTAX
trans-unit.target: 語法

trans-unit.source: Path (Default)
trans-unit.target: 路徑 （預設值）

trans-unit.source: LiteralPath
trans-unit.target: 常值路徑

trans-unit.source: DESCRIPTION
trans-unit.target: 描述

trans-unit.source: The **Clear-Item** cmdlet clears the content of an item, but it does not delete the item.
trans-unit.target: **Clear-item** cmdlet 清除某個項目的內容，但不會刪除項目。

trans-unit.source: For example, the **Clear-Item** cmdlet can delete the value of a variable, but it does not delete the variable.
trans-unit.target: 例如， **Clear-item** cmdlet 可以刪除變數的值，但不會刪除變數。

trans-unit.source: The value that used to represent a cleared item is defined by each Windows PowerShell provider.
trans-unit.target: 用來代表已清除項目的值是由各個 Windows PowerShell 提供者定義。

trans-unit.source: This cmdlet is similar to Clear-Content, but it works on aliases and variables, instead of files.
trans-unit.target: 此指令程式很類似於 Clear-content，但它可用於別名和變數，而不是檔案。

trans-unit.source: EXAMPLES
trans-unit.target: 範例

trans-unit.source: Example 1: Clear the value of a variable
trans-unit.target: 範例 1︰ 清除變數的值

trans-unit.source: This command clears the value of the variable named TestVar1.
trans-unit.target: 這個命令會清除名為 TestVar1 變數的值。

trans-unit.source: The variable remains and is valid, but its value is set to null.
trans-unit.target: 變數維持有效，但其值設為 null。

trans-unit.source: The variable name is prefixed with Variable: to indicate the Windows PowerShell Variable provider.
trans-unit.target: 變數名稱前面會加上變數︰ 來指示 Windows PowerShell 變數提供者。

trans-unit.source: The alternate commands show that, to get the same result, you can switch to the Windows PowerShell Variable: drive and then run the **Clear-Item** command.
trans-unit.target: 替代命令顯示，若要取得相同的結果，您可以切換到 Windows PowerShell Variable︰ 磁碟機，然後再執行 **Clear-item** 命令。

trans-unit.source: Example 2: Clear all registry entries
trans-unit.target: 範例 2︰ 清除所有登錄項目

trans-unit.source: This command clears all registry entries in the MyKey subkey, but only after prompting you to confirm your intent.
trans-unit.target: 這個命令會清除所有登錄項目在 MyKey 子機碼，但只有在提示您確認意圖之後。

trans-unit.source: It does not delete the MyKey subkey or affect any other registry keys or entries.
trans-unit.target: 它不會刪除 MyKey 子機碼或影響任何其他的登錄機碼或項目。

trans-unit.source: You can use the **Include** and **Exclude** parameters to identify particular registry keys, but you cannot use them to identify registry entries.
trans-unit.target: 您可以使用 **包含** 和 **排除** 參數來識別特定的登錄機碼，但是您無法使用它們來識別登錄項目。

trans-unit.source: To delete particular registry entries, use the Remove-ItemProperty cmdlet.
trans-unit.target: 若要刪除特定的登錄項目，使用 Remove-itemproperty cmdlet。

trans-unit.source: To delete the value of a registry entry, use the Clear-ItemPropertycmdlet.
trans-unit.target: 若要刪除的登錄項目值，請使用清除 ItemPropertycmdlet。

trans-unit.source: PARAMETERS
trans-unit.target: 參數

trans-unit.source: -Confirm
trans-unit.target: -Confirm

trans-unit.source: Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet.Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet.
trans-unit.target: 會提示您進行確認，然後再執行此指令程式。會提示您進行確認，然後再執行此指令程式。

trans-unit.source: -Credential
trans-unit.target: -Credential

trans-unit.source: Specifies a user account that has permission to perform this action.
trans-unit.target: 指定具有執行此動作權限的使用者帳戶。

trans-unit.source: The default is the current user.
trans-unit.target: 預設為目前使用者。

trans-unit.source: Type a user name, such as User01 or Domain01\User01, or enter a **PSCredential** object, such as one generated by the Get-Credential cmdlet.
trans-unit.target: 輸入使用者名稱，例如 User01 或 Domain01\User01，或輸入 **PSCredential** 物件，例如 Get-credential cmdlet 產生的物件。

trans-unit.source: If you type a user name, you will be prompted for a password.
trans-unit.target: 若您輸入使用者名稱，將會提示您輸入密碼。

trans-unit.source: This parameter is not supported by any providers installed with Windows PowerShell.
trans-unit.target: 與 Windows PowerShell 一起安裝的任何提供者皆不支援此參數。

trans-unit.source: -Exclude
trans-unit.target: -排除

trans-unit.source: Specifies, as a string array, items to exclude.
trans-unit.target: 以字串陣列，指定要排除的項目。

trans-unit.source: The value of this parameter qualifies the *Path* parameter.
trans-unit.target: 此參數的值會限定 *路徑* 參數。

trans-unit.source: Enter a path element or pattern, such as *.txt.
trans-unit.target: 輸入路徑元素或模式，例如 *.txt。

trans-unit.source: Wildcards are permitted.
trans-unit.target: 允許使用萬用字元。

trans-unit.source: -Filter
trans-unit.target: 篩選器

trans-unit.source: Specifies a filter in the provider's format or language.
trans-unit.target: 以提供者的格式或語言指定篩選。

trans-unit.source: The value of this parameter qualifies the *Path* parameter.
trans-unit.target: 此參數的值會限定 *路徑* 參數。

trans-unit.source: The syntax of the filter, including the use of wildcards, depends on the provider.
trans-unit.target: 篩選的語法 (包括是否使用萬用字元) 取決於提供者。

trans-unit.source: Filters are more efficient than other parameters, because the provider applies them when the cmdlet gets the objects, rather than having Windows PowerShell filter the objects after they are retrieved.
trans-unit.target: 篩選會比其他參數更有效率，因為提供者時套用此 cmdlet 會取得物件，而不是讓 Windows PowerShell 物件後篩選擷取。

trans-unit.source: -Force
trans-unit.target: -Force

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the cmdlet clears items that cannot otherwise be changed, such as read- only aliases.
trans-unit.target: 指出 cmdlet 清除無法變更，例如唯讀別名的項目。

trans-unit.source: The cmdlet cannot clear constants.
trans-unit.target: Cmdlet 無法清除常數。

trans-unit.source: Implementation varies from provider to provider.
trans-unit.target: 實作會依提供者而異。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see about_Providers.
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱 about_Providers。

trans-unit.source: The cmdlet cannot override security restrictions, even when the *Force* parameter is used.
trans-unit.target: 此指令程式無法覆寫安全性限制，即使 *Force* 參數使用。

trans-unit.source: -Include
trans-unit.target: -Include

trans-unit.source: Specifies, as a string array, items to that this cmdlet clears.
trans-unit.target: 指定為字串陣列，這個指令程式會清除的項目。

trans-unit.source: The value of this parameter qualifies the *Path* parameter.
trans-unit.target: 此參數的值會限定 *路徑* 參數。

trans-unit.source: Enter a path element or pattern, such as *.txt.
trans-unit.target: 輸入路徑元素或模式，例如 *.txt。

trans-unit.source: Wildcards are permitted.
trans-unit.target: 允許使用萬用字元。

trans-unit.source: -LiteralPath
trans-unit.target: -LiteralPath

trans-unit.source: Specifies the path to the items being cleared.
trans-unit.target: 指定要清除之項目的路徑。

trans-unit.source: Unlike *Path*, the value of the *LiteralPath* parameter is used exactly as it is typed.
trans-unit.target: 不同於 *路徑*, ，值 *LiteralPath* 完全依照其輸入，使用參數。

trans-unit.source: No characters are interpreted as wildcards.
trans-unit.target: 沒有字元會被視為萬用字元。

trans-unit.source: If the path includes escape characters, enclose it in single quotation marks.
trans-unit.target: 如果路徑包含逸出字元，請將它括在單引號中。

trans-unit.source: Single quotation marks tell *wps_2* not to interpret any characters as escape sequences.
trans-unit.target: 單引號告知 *wps_2* 不要將任何字元視為逸出序列。

trans-unit.source: -Path
trans-unit.target: -Path

trans-unit.source: Specifies the path to the items being cleared.
trans-unit.target: 指定要清除之項目的路徑。

trans-unit.source: Wildcards are permitted.
trans-unit.target: 允許使用萬用字元。

trans-unit.source: This parameter is required, but the parameter name (Path) is optional.
trans-unit.target: 這個參數是必要的但是參數名稱 （路徑） 為選擇性。

trans-unit.source: -UseTransaction
trans-unit.target: -UseTransaction

trans-unit.source: Includes the command in the active transaction.
trans-unit.target: 將命令加入使用中交易。

trans-unit.source: This parameter is valid only when a transaction is in progress.
trans-unit.target: 只有交易為處理中狀態時，此參數才有效。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see Includes the command in the active transaction.
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱包含使用中交易中的命令。

trans-unit.source: NOTES
trans-unit.target: 附註

trans-unit.source: The **Clear-Item** cmdlet is supported only by several Windows PowerShell providers, including the Alias, Environment, Function, Registry, and Variable providers.
trans-unit.target: **Clear-item** 指令程式僅支援數個 Windows PowerShell 提供者，包括別名、 環境、 函式、 登錄，以及變數提供者。

trans-unit.source: As such, you can use **Clear-Item** to delete the content of items in the provider namespaces.
trans-unit.target: 因此，您可以使用 **Clear-item** 刪除提供者命名空間中的項目內容。

trans-unit.source: You cannot use **Clear-Item** to delete the contents of a file, because the Windows PowerShell FileSystem provider does not support this cmdlet.
trans-unit.target: 您不能使用 **Clear-item** 刪除檔案的內容，因為 Windows PowerShell FileSystem 提供者不支援這個指令程式。

trans-unit.source: To clear files, use the **Clear-Content**.
trans-unit.target: 若要清除檔案，請使用 **Clear-content**。

trans-unit.source: You can also refer to **Clear-Item** by its built-in alias, cli.
trans-unit.target: 您也可以參考 **Clear-item** 內建的別名，cli。

trans-unit.source: For more information, type `Get-Help about_Aliases`.
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請鍵入 `Get-Help about_Aliases`。

trans-unit.source: The Clear-Item cmdlet is designed to work with the data exposed by any provider.
trans-unit.target: Clear-Item Cmdlet 是針對與任何提供者公開的資料搭配使用所設計。

trans-unit.source: To list the providers available in your session, type "Get-PsProvider".
trans-unit.target: 若要列出工作階段中可用的提供者，請輸入 "Get-PsProvider"。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see about_Providers.
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱 about_Providers。
